## 1. Executive Summary

The **Login & Signup Module** is the secure gateway into the Odoo POS Cafe ecosystem — a complete restaurant Point of Sale system. This module authenticates and routes four distinct user roles into their dedicated workspaces, functioning not as a generic form page but as an **intelligent onboarding portal for a cafe operating system**.

### Module Objectives

| Objective | Implementation |
|-----------|---------------|
| **Secure Authentication** | bcrypt (12 salt rounds) + JWT (7-day expiry) + httpOnly cookies |
| **4-Role RBAC** | Cashier, Kitchen, Customer, Manager — each with unique redirects |
| **Premium UX** | Light-mode, cafe-inspired, glassmorphism, microanimations |
| **Real-Time Validation** | Client-side + Server-side dual validation with inline feedback |
| **Production Security** | Rate limiting, input sanitization, credential isolation, XSS prevention |
| **Responsive Design** | Desktop split-view, tablet compressed, mobile stacked |

### Technology Stack Decision Matrix

| Layer | Technology | Version | Justification |
|-------|-----------|---------|---------------|
| **Frontend Framework** | React | 18.3.1 | Component model, hooks, Context API |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | 5.4.14 | Sub-second HMR, fast builds, ESM-native |
| **CSS Framework** | Tailwind CSS | 3.4.17 | Utility-first, custom design tokens, JIT |
| **Routing** | React Router | 6.28.2 | Declarative routing, protected routes |
| **HTTP Client** | Axios | 1.7.9 | Interceptors for token management |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | 0.468.0 | Tree-shakable, lightweight SVG icons |
| **Notifications** | React Hot Toast | 2.4.1 | Minimal, performant toast system |
| **Backend Runtime** | Node.js | 20+ | V8 engine, non-blocking I/O |
| **Server Framework** | Express | 4.21.2 | Middleware ecosystem, proven stability |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas | 8.9.5 (Mongoose) | Flexible schema, cloud-hosted, auto-scaling |
| **Password Hashing** | bcryptjs | 2.4.3 | Constant-time comparison, CPU-bound security |
| **Token Auth** | jsonwebtoken | 9.0.2 | Industry-standard JWT, RS256 support |
| **Input Validation** | express-validator | 7.2.1 | Chain-based, sanitization, custom rules |
| **Rate Limiting** | express-rate-limit | 7.5.0 | Brute-force protection, sliding window |

