## 3. User Roles & RBAC Matrix

### Role Definitions

| Role | Value | Description | Primary Workspace | Conditional Fields |
|------|-------|-------------|-------------------|-------------------|
| **POS Staff / Cashier** | `cashier` | Manages tables, orders, billing | `/pos/floor` | `employeeId` |
| **Kitchen Staff** | `kitchen` | Receives tickets, updates preparation | `/kitchen` | `employeeId` |
| **Customer** | `customer` | Tracks orders, self-ordering | `/customer` | `phone` |
| **Manager / Admin** | `manager` | Full configuration, reporting, staff mgmt | `/dashboard` | `businessName` |

### Role-Permission Matrix

| Permission | Cashier | Kitchen | Customer | Manager |
|-----------|:-------:|:-------:|:--------:|:-------:|
| POS Floor View | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Order Creation | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ (self) | ✅ |
| Payment Processing | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Kitchen Display | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Order Status Update | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Customer Display | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Self-Ordering | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Product Management | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Floor Plan Config | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Payment Methods Config | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Sales Reports | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Session Management | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |

### Role-Based Redirect Map

```javascript
// AuthContext.jsx — getRoleRedirectPath()
const getRoleRedirectPath = useCallback((role) => {
  const paths = {
    cashier: '/pos/floor',     // → POS Terminal Floor View
    kitchen: '/kitchen',       // → Kitchen Display Dashboard
    customer: '/customer',     // → Customer Self-Order Portal
    manager: '/dashboard',     // → Management Dashboard
  };
  return paths[role] || '/dashboard';
}, []);
```

### Role-Based Route Protection

| Route Pattern | Allowed Roles | Component | Guard |
|-------------|---------------|-----------|-------|
| `/login` | Public (unauthenticated only) | `AuthPage` | Redirect if authed |
| `/signup` | Public (unauthenticated only) | `AuthPage` | Redirect if authed |
| `/dashboard` | All authenticated | `Dashboard` | `ProtectedRoute` |
| `/pos/*` | `cashier`, `manager` | `Dashboard` | `ProtectedRoute` + role check |
| `/kitchen` | `kitchen`, `manager` | `Dashboard` | `ProtectedRoute` + role check |
| `/customer/*` | `customer` | `Dashboard` | `ProtectedRoute` + role check |

