### State Management Architecture

| State Layer | Tool | Scope | Data |
|-------------|------|-------|------|
| **Global Auth** | React Context + useCallback | App-wide | `user`, `isAuthenticated`, `loading` |
| **Form State** | useState | AuthCard component | `formData`, `errors`, `touched` |
| **UI State** | useState | AuthCard component | `showPassword`, `loading`, `termsAccepted` |
| **API Layer** | Axios + Interceptors | Service layer | Token attachment, 401 auto-redirect |
| **Persistence** | localStorage | Browser | `pos_token`, `pos_user` |

### Context Provider Values

```javascript
// AuthContext.jsx — Provider value
{
  user,                  // User object or null
  loading,               // Boolean — initial auth check
  isAuthenticated,       // Boolean — auth state
  login(credentials),    // async Function — handles login flow
  signup(userData),      // async Function — handles signup flow
  logout(),              // async Function — clears tokens + state
  getRoleRedirectPath(role), // Function — returns route string
}
```

