## 9. Validation System

### Dual-Layer Validation Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["User Input"] --> B["Client-Side Validation"]
    B -->|"Error"| C["Inline Error Display"]
    B -->|"Valid"| D["API Request"]
    D --> E["Server-Side Validation"]
    E -->|"Error"| F["Toast Error Notification"]
    E -->|"Valid"| G["Database Operation"]
    G -->|"Constraint Error"| F
    G -->|"Success"| H["Response to Client"]

    style B fill:#FEF3C7,stroke:#F59E0B
    style E fill:#DBEAFE,stroke:#3B82F6
```

### Client-Side Validation Rules

| Field | Function | Rule | Error Message |
|-------|----------|------|--------------|
| `fullName` | `isValidName()` | 2-50 chars, trimmed | "Name must be 2-50 characters" |
| `username` | `isValidUsername()` | `^[a-zA-Z0-9_]{3,30}$` | "Letters, numbers, underscores only (3-30 chars)" |
| `email` | `isValidEmail()` | `^\S+@\S+\.\S+$` | "Please enter a valid email" |
| `password` | `isValidPassword()` | `length >= 6` | "Minimum 6 characters required" |
| `confirmPassword` | Custom match | `value === password` | "Passwords do not match" |
| `role` | Non-empty | `value !== ''` | "Please select a role" |

### Validation Triggering Strategy

| Event | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| **onBlur** | Mark field as `touched`, validate immediately |
| **onChange (touched)** | Re-validate on every keystroke after first blur |
| **onChange (untouched)** | No validation — let user complete input first |
| **onSubmit** | Force-touch all fields, validate everything |

---

## 10. Security Architecture

### Security Measures Comparison

| Threat | Protection | Implementation |
|--------|-----------|---------------|
| **Brute Force** | Rate Limiting | 50 requests / 15 minutes per IP via `express-rate-limit` |
| **Password Theft** | bcrypt Hashing | 12 salt rounds, constant-time comparison |
| **XSS Token Theft** | httpOnly Cookie | Cookie inaccessible to JavaScript |
| **CSRF** | SameSite Cookie | `sameSite: 'lax'` prevents cross-origin requests |
| **Injection** | Input Sanitization | `express-validator` + Mongoose schema validation |
| **Data Exposure** | `select: false` | Password never returned in queries |
| **Credential Leak** | `.env` isolation | MongoDB URI + JWT secret server-side only |
| **Transport** | HTTPS enforcement | `secure: true` cookie flag in production |
| **Duplicate Accounts** | Unique Indexes | Unique constraints on `email` and `username` |
| **Privilege Escalation** | Role Guard | `authorize()` middleware checks `req.user.role` |
| **Deactivated Access** | Active Check | Both `protect` middleware and login route check `isActive` |

### Credential Storage Strategy

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│          server/.env (PRIVATE)        │
│  MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://...       │
│  JWT_SECRET=odoo_pos_cafe_...        │
│  JWT_EXPIRE=7d                       │
│  NODE_ENV=development                │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘
         ▲ Never in client code
         │ Never in git repository
         │ Never in browser console
```

