## 13. Error Handling Matrix

### Complete Error State Table

| Error Type | Source | HTTP | User Sees | UI Treatment |
|-----------|--------|:----:|-----------|-------------|
| Empty required field | Client | — | Inline: "Field is required" | Red border + dot indicator |
| Invalid email format | Client | — | Inline: "Please enter a valid email" | Red border + message |
| Username bad chars | Client | — | Inline: "Letters, numbers, underscores only" | Red border |
| Password too short | Client | — | Inline: "Minimum 6 characters required" | Red border + strength bar |
| Password mismatch | Client | — | Inline: "Passwords do not match" | Red border on confirm field |
| No role selected | Client | — | Inline: "Please select a role" | Red dot below role grid |
| Terms not accepted | Client | — | Inline below checkbox | Red text |
| Duplicate email | Server | 400 | Toast: "An account with this email already exists" | Toast error notification |
| Duplicate username | Server | 400 | Toast: "This username is already taken" | Toast error notification |
| Invalid credentials | Server | 401 | Toast: "Invalid credentials — user not found" | Toast + general error box |
| Wrong password | Server | 401 | Toast: "Invalid credentials — incorrect password" | Toast + general error box |
| Account deactivated | Server | 403 | Toast: "Account deactivated. Contact administrator." | Toast error |
| Rate limited | Server | 429 | Toast: "Too many requests. Try again in 15 min." | Toast error |
| Server down | Network | — | Toast: "Login failed. Please try again." | Toast error |
| Expired token | Server | 401 | Auto-redirect to `/login` | Clear localStorage |

