## 14. Performance Strategy

### Frontend Performance Optimizations

| Strategy | Implementation | Impact |
|----------|---------------|--------|
| **Component Extraction** | `InputField` defined outside `AuthCard` | Prevents remount on every keystroke |
| **useCallback Memoization** | `handleChange`, `handleBlur`, `login`, `signup`, `logout` | Stable references, no unnecessary re-renders |
| **CSS-Only Animations** | `transform`, `opacity` only | GPU-accelerated, no layout thrashing |
| **Tree-Shaking Icons** | Individual lucide-react imports | Only used icons in bundle |
| **Vite HMR** | Sub-second hot module replacement | Fast development cycles |
| **Tailwind JIT** | Just-in-time CSS compilation | Minimal CSS bundle size |
| **Font Preconnect** | `rel="preconnect"` for Google Fonts | Faster font loading |
| **Reduced Motion** | `prefers-reduced-motion` media query | All animations disabled |
| **Lazy State Updates** | Validation only on touched fields | No validation on initial render |

### Backend Performance Optimizations

| Strategy | Implementation |
|----------|---------------|
| **`select: false`** on password | Password never loaded unless explicitly requested |
| **MongoDB Indexes** | Unique indexes on email/username for O(log n) lookups |
| **Rate Limiting** | Prevents server overload from brute-force |
| **`validateBeforeSave: false`** on login | Skips re-validation when updating lastLogin |
| **JSON limit** | `express.json({ limit: '10mb' })` prevents payload abuse |

---

## 15. Accessibility Support

### WCAG 2.1 Compliance

| Requirement | Implementation |
|-------------|---------------|
| **Keyboard Navigation** | All form elements, buttons, and role cards are focusable via Tab |
| **Focus Indicators** | `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-cafe-500/30 focus:ring-offset-2` on CTA |
| **Semantic Labels** | All inputs have explicit `<label htmlFor>` associations |
| **ARIA Password Toggle** | `aria-label="Show password"` / `aria-label="Hide password"` |
| **ARIA Role Selection** | `aria-pressed={isActive}` + `aria-label="Select role: ..."` |
| **Color Contrast** | Stone-900 on cream-50 = **13.5:1** ratio (exceeds AAA) |
| **Error Announcements** | Error messages in DOM, associated with fields |
| **Reduced Motion** | `prefers-reduced-motion` disables all animations |
| **Touch Targets** | Buttons minimum 44px height, role cards spacious tap area |

