## 16. Testing Scenarios

### Critical Test Cases

| # | Scenario | Steps | Expected Result | Priority |
|---|---------|-------|-----------------|:--------:|
| 1 | **Successful signup** | Fill all fields correctly, select role, accept terms, submit | 201 response, redirect to role page | 🔴 High |
| 2 | **Successful login** | Enter valid email + password | 200 response, redirect to correct role page | 🔴 High |
| 3 | **Login with username** | Enter username instead of email | Resolves user, logs in successfully | 🔴 High |
| 4 | **Duplicate email** | Register with existing email | 400 error, "email already exists" toast | 🔴 High |
| 5 | **Duplicate username** | Register with existing username | 400 error, "username taken" toast | 🔴 High |
| 6 | **Wrong password** | Login with correct email, wrong password | 401 error, "incorrect password" | 🔴 High |
| 7 | **User not found** | Login with non-existent account | 401 error, "user not found" | 🟡 Medium |
| 8 | **Password mismatch** | Signup with different confirm password | Inline error, form doesn't submit | 🟡 Medium |
| 9 | **Weak password** | Enter "123" as password | Strength meter shows "Weak" in red | 🟡 Medium |
| 10 | **Mode switching** | Toggle between Login and Signup | Smooth transition, errors reset | 🟡 Medium |
| 11 | **Role selection** | Click each role card | Active state, conditional fields appear | 🟡 Medium |
| 12 | **Manager conditional** | Select Manager role | Business Name field appears | 🟡 Medium |
| 13 | **Cashier conditional** | Select Cashier role | Employee ID field appears | 🟡 Medium |
| 14 | **Customer conditional** | Select Customer role | Phone field appears | 🟡 Medium |
| 15 | **Empty form submit** | Click submit without filling | All required fields show errors | 🟡 Medium |
| 16 | **Auth persistence** | Login, reload page | User stays authenticated | 🔴 High |
| 17 | **Logout** | Click logout button | Tokens cleared, redirect to login | 🔴 High |
| 18 | **Protected route** | Navigate to /dashboard without login | Redirect to /login | 🔴 High |
| 19 | **Role guard** | Cashier navigates to /kitchen | Redirect to /unauthorized | 🟡 Medium |
| 20 | **Rate limiting** | Send 51 requests in 15 minutes | 429 "Too many requests" | 🟢 Low |
| 21 | **Deactivated user** | Login with isActive=false account | 403 "Account deactivated" | 🟢 Low |
| 22 | **Mobile responsive** | Open on mobile viewport | Stacked layout, no overflow | 🟡 Medium |
| 23 | **Password visibility** | Toggle show/hide on password field | Input type switches, icon changes | 🟢 Low |
| 24 | **Keyboard flow** | Tab through all fields + submit | Complete cycle works without mouse | 🟢 Low |

